Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:08.08,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}都聯繫在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:14.31,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}肯定很快就會相會
